            Hello, world! <br />
            My name is Lindsey Shepard, and this is my personal page. <br /><br />
            In July I began a new chapter of my life by participating in Microsoft’s Software and Systems Academy (MSSA)
            for Cloud Development. This was exciting and scary at the same time because I never walked down the road of software development. In January of 2019 I transitioned out of the United States
